data.description: Nice home in the heart of Fernley. Owners have done some updating that includes new plumbing throughout the home, 3 new double pane windows, new dishwasher, new garbage disposal, new swamp cooler, newly installed gutters, new wall paint, backyard fence completed for privacy and pets. This home has a great sized yard with 2 storage sheds that stay. A nice large front deck that creates a great outdoor space.
